About this item

  • Rechargeable LED Wall Mounted Lights. Lightbiz LED wall mounted lamps built-in a 3000mAh rechargeable battery. The working time after full charge determined based on brightness. Fully charged less than 4hrs can work for up to 24hrs in medium brightness, maximum brightness is up to 15hrs. Portable cordless wall light sconces with USB-C charging port. NOTE: Please Install The Lamp Holder First And Bond It To The Wall For At Least 4 Hours Before Installing The Lamp Body. Wet Weather, Uneven Wall, or Dust May All Affect The Bonding Performance Of The Lamp Holder.
  • LED Wall Lights with Button&Remote Control. Two control methods for this magnetic wall lights which are button control and remote control. Lightbiz LED wall sconce also comes with a remote. Eliminated the hassle of button control. You can complete all settings through the remote control: ON/OFF; 3 color temperature switching; brightness adjustment and Timing.
  • 3 Color Temperature & Dimmable Wall Sconces. Button control and remote control both can switch the color temperature(3000K-4500K-6000K). Also two ways for dimming this magnetic wall lights. Button control: Stepless(Long press). Remote control: ①stepless(Button”+”&”-”); ②4 levels: 10%,40%,80%,100%. You can choose the color temperature and the brightness based on different usage scenarios.
  • 360° Free Rotations Magnetic Ball. This bedside lamp use magnetic technology. The lamp body and lamp holder are adsorbed by a magnetic iron ball, so the lamp body can rotate at any angle. You can take it off the wall in 1s and use it as flashlight, removable light, portable light, emergency light etc. Adjust any angle according to your usage scenario.
  • Easy to Install. LED wall lamp is Tools-Free installation: This led wall reading lights come with magnetic mount and strong 3M adhesive. It is easy to remove the light from the magnet mount for charging.(But also come with screw, If you want to permanently fix the lamp in a certain position, you can use screw mounting.)
  • Application&Lightbiz Services. Our universal multifunctional wall lamp is small&simple design but modern&widely application. This magnetic wall light is widely used in wardrobes, TV walls, bedside, hallway, cabinet, closet, stairway, bedrooms, stairs and corridors. It's super bright but Eye-Caring, perfect for reading, working, study, makeup. Please feel free to contact us for any product issue. Better Light, Better Life !

    Product Description

    Lightbiz LED Wall Mounted Lights

    Wall Lamps & Sconces with simple design but widely application:

    This universal wall lamp is creativity, art, simplicity and personality. It is widely used in bedside, wardrobes,

    TV walls, living rooms, bedrooms, stairs, corridors, closet, cabinet, bath, hallway.

    The Lamps can be also used as flashlight, removable light, portable light, emergency light.

    Indoor wall mount LED lamps is perfect for reading, working, study, makeup.

    Two installation ways for this magnetic wall light:

    1. Comes with magnetic mount and strong 3M adhesive. Tear off the adhesive tape at the bottom of the lamp holder,

    use strong adhesive to install the holder on a smooth and clean surface, and then use magnetism to adsorb and install the lamp body.

    2. Comes with screws and holes on the lamp holder. If the surface of the lamp you are installing is not smooth and clean,

    you can use screws to reinforce the installation.

    Product Information:

    Color temperature: 3000K-4500K-6000K

    Power: 4W

    Battery Capacity: 3000mAh

    Voltage: DC 5V 1A

    Material: Plastic/Metal

    Control method: Button/Remote

    Full charge time: About 4 hours

    Charging: Red light

    Fully charged: Green light

    CAUTION:

    Before using 3M adhesive for installation, please ensure that the surface being installed is clean, flat, and smooth. Otherwise, it will affect the performance of 3M adhesive and cause the lamp to fall off. NOTE: Please Install The Lamp Holder First And Bond It To The Wall For At Least 4 Hours Before Installing The Lamp Body. Wet Weather, Uneven Wall, or Dust May All Affect The Bonding Performance Of The Lamp Holder.

    Please use screws carefully for installation reinforcement, as it will inevitably damage the surface being installed.

    Accessories:

    Lamp body x 3

    Lamp holder x 3

    USB-C Charging Cable x 2

    Remote control x 2

    User manual x 1

    From the manufacturer

    LED Wall Mounted Lights with Remote

    The Wall Lamps & Sconces with simple design but widely application.

    This universal wall lamp is creativity, art, simplicity and personality. It is widely used in bedside, wardrobes, TV walls, living rooms, bedrooms, stairs, corridors, closet, cabinet, bath, hallway.

    It can be also used as artwork lighting, flashlight, removable light, portable light, emergency light. Indoor wall mount LED lamps is perfect for reading, working, study, makeup.

    Rechargeable Wireless LED Wall Sconces

    Charging Description:

    Charging: Red light indicator

    Fully charged: Green light indicator

    Charging port type: USB-C

    Charging time: About 4 hours

    After fully charged, 24H battery life in medium brightbess, up to 15H battery life in maximum brightness.

    3 Color Temperature Switching

    You can switch the Color Temperature by button & remote control for this magnetic wall lights.

    Cool Light(6000K) Suitable for Working

    Natural Light(4500K) Suitable for Reading

    Warm Light（3000k) Suitable for Rest

    Brightness Adjustable Wall Sconces Lamp

    According to different usage scenarios, you can also set different brightness based on your needs by button & remote control.

    Button Control: Long press for the stepless brightness adjustment.

    Remote Control: Single press the "+" "-" button for the stepless brightness adjustment; Single press the "10%" "50%" "100%" Button for 3 Level brightness adjustment.

    Two Installation Ways for the Magnetic 360° Free Rotations LED Wall Lamp

    1. Comes with magnetic mount and strong 3M adhesive. Tear off the adhesive tape at the bottom of the lamp holder, use strong adhesive to install the holder on a smooth and clean surface, and then use magnetism to adsorb and install the lamp body.

    2. Comes with screws and holes on the lamp holder. If the surface of the lamp you are installing is not smooth and clean, you can use screws to reinforce the installation.

    CAUTION:

    Before using 3M adhesive for installation, please ensure that the surface being installed is clean, flat, and smooth. Otherwise, it will affect the performance of 3M adhesive and cause the lamp to fall off. Please use screws carefully for installation reinforcement, as it will inevitably damage the surface being installed.
